15 WHEREAS, physician anesthesiologists are recognized leaders who are committed to safe
16 and high-quality patient care, educating patients on anesthesia safety and reducing the risks
17 of complications.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
19 recognize January 26 to February 1, 2025, as Physician Anesthesiologists Week at the state
20 capitol.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
22 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia Society
23 of Anesthesiologists, the public, and the press.
